{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-people-page-js","path":"/speakers/edward-anderson","result":{"data":{"people":{"parent":{"html":"<h2>About</h2>\n<p>Edward Anderson is the Senior Technology and Resilience Specialist for the <a href=\"https://www.gfdrr.org/en\">Global Facility for Disaster Reduction and Recovery</a> based in Washington DC. His focus is on leveraging satellite applications and emerging imaging technologies for greater resilience in development operations. This includes the Digital Earth Partnership – a multi stakeholder platform to accelerate the deployment of frontier Earth Observation tools and services for risk-informed developed. Other programs include the Resilience Academy, which builds local skills and services adopting satellite, internet of things, community feedback and drone monitoring technologies to address unplanned urbanization in Africa. Edward participates on the EU’s Drones in Humanitarian Action Expert Working Group and holds Master’s degrees in both aerospace engineering and international economics and international relations.</p>"},"id":"6eb41b22-14db-532c-9069-aa74471d620d","title":"Edward Anderson","company":"World Bank","role":"Senior Technology and Resilience Specialist for the Global Facility for Disaster Reduction and Recovery","twitter":null,"pronouns":null,"avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/1b50a/edward-anderson.jpg","srcSet":"/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/c904d/edward-anderson.jpg 160w,\n/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/b95ad/edward-anderson.jpg 320w,\n/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/1b50a/edward-anderson.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/c6aca/edward-anderson.webp 160w,\n/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/0a0af/edward-anderson.webp 320w,\n/static/197404015141e2eb52e31c8abf5c2408/8ae69/edward-anderson.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":640}}},"events":[{"role":"panelists","event":{"parent":{"html":"<p>Perspectives on the application of satellite data to advancing sustainable development. The panel will discuss how Covid and resulting economic effects have altered development priorities and practices; adapting their work to the climate crisis; and where earth insights are providing the most value.</p>"},"cId":"28-1050-the-implementers","title":"The Implementers","slug":"28-1050-the-implementers","type":"Panel","room":"The Forum","date":"2022-09-28 10:50","people":{"hosts":[],"moderators":[{"title":"Nicki McGoh","slug":"nicki-mcgoh","group":"main"}],"panelists":[{"title":"David Moinina Sengeh","isVoid":true},{"title":"Carrie Stokes","slug":"carrie-stokes","group":"main"},{"title":"Edward Anderson","slug":"edward-anderson","group":"main"},{"title":"Hanna Camp","slug":"hanna-camp","group":"main"}],"facilitators":[],"speakers":[]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"edward-anderson"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2576411084","446613330","692872813"]}